U planinama postadosmo vuci

5
00:04:04,955 --> 00:04:08,555
Slogan nam je:
Sloboda il' smrt!

6
00:04:08,555 --> 00:04:12,151
otiiemo u dolinu
s pukama u ruci

7
00:04:12,151 --> 00:04:15,031
spremni za boj.

8
00:04:15,790 --> 00:04:19,110
Meu rtvama
koje osvetu ekaju

9
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:22,589
meu onim mravim licima

10
00:04:22,629 --> 00:04:26,508
naplatiemo im
na barikadama

11
00:04:26,508 --> 00:04:29,585
metak za metak.

12
00:04:29,585 --> 00:04:35,184
Naplatiemo im na barikadama...

13
00:04:47,058 --> 00:04:49,378
Rat je gotov!

14
00:05:11,330 --> 00:05:13,248
Zato?

15
00:05:15,848 --> 00:05:19,087
Za nama! Trkom!

16
00:05:33,641 --> 00:05:36,761
Nikada nisam ni kravu upucao!

17
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:39,078
Hou i ja jednu.

18
00:05:47,436 --> 00:05:50,595
Pazi, nemoj da te ubiju!

19
00:05:50,634 --> 00:05:55,353
eno, uplasti to seno
da ne pokisne!

20
00:05:55,633 --> 00:05:57,073
ta ti hoe?

21
00:05:57,114 --> 00:06:01,311
Hou i ja jednu.
Ja sam sek'o telefonske ice.

22
00:06:01,311 --> 00:06:07,109
Tigre, daj i meni jednu!
Obeao si!

23
00:06:07,468 --> 00:06:09,786
Leonida, dolazi 'vamo!

24
00:06:11,267 --> 00:06:13,585
Uzmi i okvir.

25
00:06:14,427 --> 00:06:17,025
Kuda e, Leonida?
-Hou i ja da ih ubijem!

26
00:06:56,810 --> 00:07:00,128
...iz Mlanske radio stanice
koju smo upravo okupirali.

27
00:07:00,688 --> 00:07:04,646
Napokon slobodan, Milano
pozdravlja italijanski narod.

28
00:07:04,686 --> 00:07:09,285
Ovo je komanda
Partizanke Brigade "Giacomo Matteotti"

29
00:07:09,285 --> 00:07:13,364
U ovom momentu sree...

30
00:07:13,403 --> 00:07:16,842
...nae misli su sa onima
koji su pali na svakom frontu...

31
00:07:16,842 --> 00:07:21,080
...u borbi protiv nacistikih varvara.

32
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:23,000
Ali, pre svega...

33
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:26,519
Leonida! ta radi ovde?

34
00:07:26,998 --> 00:07:29,397
Nisam videla da ulazi.

35
00:07:30,797 --> 00:07:34,835
Ba si ozbiljan!
ta e ti ta puka?

36
00:07:34,835 --> 00:07:36,754
Skloni se!

37
00:07:37,474 --> 00:07:40,392
iveo Staljin!
-Jesil' poludeo?

38
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:49,789
iveo Staljin!

39
00:07:52,788 --> 00:07:54,708
Attila i Regina!

40
00:07:56,387 --> 00:07:58,306
Attila i Regina!

41
00:08:10,501 --> 00:08:15,499
Setite se onog dana aprilskog...

42
00:08:16,060 --> 00:08:21,817
i dugog voza koji je...

43
00:09:54,821 --> 00:09:56,742
Regina!

44
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:01,460
Regina!

45
00:10:01,460 --> 00:10:03,218
Attila!

46
00:10:10,057 --> 00:10:13,094
Ovde sam!

47
00:10:18,054 --> 00:10:19,693
Dolazi ovamo!

48
00:10:23,612 --> 00:10:25,530
Sam si to traio!

49
00:10:33,207 --> 00:10:35,127
Laste se vratie.

50
00:10:40,525 --> 00:10:42,443
Molim te, saekaj.

51
00:11:02,677 --> 00:11:05,396
Zna li da je
moj deda umro ba tu?

52
00:11:27,428 --> 00:11:29,346
Sedi!

53
00:11:45,701 --> 00:11:49,619
Zna li da u Americi
svaka krava ima svoje pojilo?

54
00:11:49,619 --> 00:11:53,577
Ali, to su amerike krave,
one ive udobno.

55
00:11:54,217 --> 00:11:58,775
Da li bi iao
u Ameriku, Leonida?

56
00:11:58,775 --> 00:12:00,694
Zovi me Olmo.

57
00:12:02,375 --> 00:12:06,892
Nisi vie Leonida?
- Partizansko ime mi je Olmo.

58
00:12:06,892 --> 00:12:10,732
Zna li ko je bio Olmo?
- On je bio najhrabriji!

59
00:12:12,330 --> 00:12:14,249
Najhrabriji...

60
00:12:17,407 --> 00:12:21,206
Pa, mali moj ratnie,
ta misli o svom gazdi?

61
00:12:21,206 --> 00:12:23,404
Nea vie gazda.

62
00:12:23,566 --> 00:12:28,125
MNOGO GODINA KASNIJE

63
00:12:29,643 --> 00:12:32,843
Verdi je mrtav!

64
00:12:37,281 --> 00:12:40,800
Giuseppe Verdi je mrtav!

65
00:13:21,184 --> 00:13:25,822
Guraj! Guraj! Guraj!

66
00:13:25,862 --> 00:13:28,902
Guraj! Guraj!
-Evo ga, izlazi!

67
00:13:38,098 --> 00:13:42,856
Hajde, guraj!

68
00:13:47,534 --> 00:13:51,732
Zatvori vrata.
-Tie, deco.

69
00:13:52,971 --> 00:13:56,890
Deak je! Deak!

70
00:13:58,089 --> 00:14:01,887
Rosina je rodila deaka!!

71
00:14:02,207 --> 00:14:04,128
Deak je!

72
00:14:18,922 --> 00:14:23,559
Deak je, deak!

73
00:14:24,239 --> 00:14:26,159
ta je s tom neodgovornom enom?

74
00:14:34,076 --> 00:14:36,235
uje li, prokletnice?

75
00:14:36,275 --> 00:14:39,354
Seljak je roen pre
sina svog gospodara!

76
00:14:39,354 --> 00:14:41,792
Trebam li da odem da izvuem bebu?

77
00:14:50,429 --> 00:14:54,987
Eleonora guraj!!
Hajde, pusti ga napolje!!

78
00:14:54,987 --> 00:14:56,907
Napni se jae!

79
00:14:58,147 --> 00:15:00,107
Hajde, guraj!

80
00:15:03,064 --> 00:15:04,905
Prokletstvo!

81
00:15:07,503 --> 00:15:09,423
Tata.

82
00:15:10,502 --> 00:15:12,420
Tata...

83
00:15:23,817 --> 00:15:26,537
Alfredo je roen!

84
00:15:26,537 --> 00:15:29,295
Dobie ime po meni!

85
00:15:29,774 --> 00:15:34,332
ta ako je devojia?
-Nije valjda?

86
00:15:35,014 --> 00:15:39,931
Misli da ne znam razliku?
Ova beba ima piu.

87
00:15:39,931 --> 00:15:42,330
Ima oi na oca.

88
00:15:43,330 --> 00:15:45,488
I novac na dedu.

89
00:15:46,048 --> 00:15:48,648
Ima piu!
Ima piu!

90
00:15:48,648 --> 00:15:51,006
Giovanni! Giovanni! Giovanni!

91
00:15:51,006 --> 00:15:53,326
ta?
-Kako je majka?

92
00:15:53,366 --> 00:15:56,286
Dobro je.
-Poljubi je u moje ime.

93
00:15:56,325 --> 00:16:02,202
"Nebesa nas poslae ovamo
kao topli letnji vetar.

94
00:16:03,002 --> 00:16:09,640
Neka u srcu ponese
vrline svojih predaka."

95
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:12,518
Ok, shvatili smo.
Giovanni!

96
00:16:12,558 --> 00:16:15,197
Da, tata?
-Pii onom tvom bratu, plejboju.

97
00:16:15,197 --> 00:16:18,197
Hajde, pii mu.
-Da, tata.

98
00:16:19,516 --> 00:16:22,635
"Ottavio..."
Ali, nema li papira??

99
00:16:23,475 --> 00:16:27,114
"Ottavio Berlinghieri,
Hotel de Ben. Lido, Venezia.

100
00:16:27,473 --> 00:16:31,192
Obavetavamo o prvoroenom
Berlinghieriju 20tom veku, taka.

101
00:16:31,592 --> 00:16:33,829
Moliu se da ne bude
kao ti, taka.

102
00:16:35,069 --> 00:16:39,187
Jesi li naao enu, znak pitanja.
Pozdrav, tata."

103
00:16:39,187 --> 00:16:41,348
Sve si zapisao?
-Naravno, tata.

104
00:16:41,348 --> 00:16:43,266
Dobro.

105
00:17:00,020 --> 00:17:02,220
Sestra Desolata je ovde!

106
00:17:05,740 --> 00:17:09,016
Dragi brate.
-Deak je.

107
00:17:09,016 --> 00:17:10,937
Bravo! Bravo!

108
00:17:11,816 --> 00:17:16,853
Iznesi sve iz kola.
Ne vraam se u samostan.

109
00:17:17,813 --> 00:17:21,692
Monsignor me ignorie,
vie mu nije stalo do mene.

110
00:17:21,732 --> 00:17:26,690
Vie mu se sviaju novopridole
Da su bar iz dobrih familija!

111
00:17:26,690 --> 00:17:31,607
uj. Onog dana, ja...
-Moj eir!

112
00:17:31,648 --> 00:17:33,568
Alfredo!

113
00:17:35,447 --> 00:17:37,367
Hvaljen neka je Gospod.

114
00:17:38,446 --> 00:17:43,404
Zaboga, ak mu je i kua
puna popova! Ne mogu im umai!

115
00:17:54,360 --> 00:17:57,478
Grbavi, ta vidi?

116
00:17:59,518 --> 00:18:03,317
Sneg je, kao za zime.

117
00:18:03,956 --> 00:18:08,834
Jo?
-Katedrala, s tornjevima.

118
00:18:08,874 --> 00:18:11,833
ta jo?
-Boce.

119
00:18:12,113 --> 00:18:14,311
Molim?
-Flae.

120
00:18:14,351 --> 00:18:20,030
ivotu, koji ti se smei...

121
00:18:22,029 --> 00:18:26,187
Gazda, to su Nebesa,
a ti si svemogui Bog.

122
00:18:26,187 --> 00:18:29,826
Eh, samo da imam kljueve!
Sveti Petar bi se lepo napio!

123
00:18:54,658 --> 00:18:56,976
Evo! Nalokaj se!

124
00:18:57,016 --> 00:19:00,574
Dosta je rada.
Da pijemo sad.

125
00:19:00,614 --> 00:19:03,694
Uzdravlje!

126
00:19:04,973 --> 00:19:08,012
Ovo je za tebe.
Nema rada danas.

127
00:19:08,012 --> 00:19:11,050
Vincenzo, ovo je specijalno vino.
Da nazdravimo.

128
00:19:11,330 --> 00:19:15,088
Hvala gazda.
-Ali, gde je Leo?

129
00:19:15,129 --> 00:19:16,889
Tamo.

130
00:19:16,929 --> 00:19:19,726
Ne...
-Daj mi to, pseto!

131
00:19:23,565 --> 00:19:26,845
Libero, zna li ko je umro?
Vidi ovu flau!

132
00:19:48,996 --> 00:19:52,395
Sudbina im je bila da se rode istog dana.

133
00:19:52,635 --> 00:19:54,673
Da nazdravimo!

134
00:19:56,314 --> 00:19:59,753
G. Alfredo, znate li
koliko D'Alcosa ima sada?

135
00:19:59,753 --> 00:20:01,792
Ne mogu ih prebrojati

136
00:20:01,792 --> 00:20:05,430
Kad sednem za sto ima nas 40.

137
00:20:05,470 --> 00:20:11,467
Hajde, Leo, razmisli!
Seljak je, al' je muko!

138
00:20:11,467 --> 00:20:14,027
Zato? Muki ne jedu?

139
00:20:16,465 --> 00:20:18,385
ta je s tobom?

140
00:20:23,783 --> 00:20:25,504
Moj je roen pre tvog.

141
00:20:25,543 --> 00:20:29,540
Svi znaju, prvo su bili
seljaci, pa gazde.

142
00:20:29,579 --> 00:20:33,618
Gazde, seljaci, sranje!
Sva roenja su u isto vreme!

143
00:20:33,618 --> 00:20:35,899
Sva, istovremeno?
- Umukni, prevrtljive!

144
00:20:37,417 --> 00:20:39,337
Hje, vi!

145
00:20:39,657 --> 00:20:44,215
ta ekate?
Rekoh vam da pijete, spadala!

146
00:21:22,521 --> 00:21:24,480
Pijte sa mnom.

147
00:21:36,955 --> 00:21:38,354
Ok, da pijemo.

148
00:21:40,754 --> 00:21:44,433
Roeni zajedno.
To neto znai.

149
00:21:47,830 --> 00:21:51,269
To znai da emo nas dvojca
umreti zajedno.

150
00:21:51,309 --> 00:21:54,189
Idi doavola,
guzice filozofska!

151
00:21:59,106 --> 00:22:01,547
Moj unuk e biti javni belenik.

152
00:22:02,106 --> 00:22:06,185
Moj e biti lopov.
-Moe da bude i pop.

153
00:22:13,300 --> 00:22:16,740
Ovo nije lokavno vino.
-Predobro je za tebe.

154
00:22:16,740 --> 00:22:18,940
Ni meni se nije svidelo.

155
00:22:20,898 --> 00:22:24,338
Rigoletto, dosta pia,
tri do gradske venice.

156
00:22:24,377 --> 00:22:29,375
Reci im da je dobio ime po meni,
Alfredo. Berlinghieri Alfredo.

157
00:22:29,375 --> 00:22:32,695
Sin Giovannia
i Eleonore Rossetti.

158
00:22:39,810 --> 00:22:43,169
Leo, kako e ga ti nazvati?

159
00:22:43,169 --> 00:22:46,528
ta? -Kako e nazvati svoje unue?

160
00:22:52,366 --> 00:22:54,286
Olmo.

161
00:22:55,086 --> 00:22:58,885
Olmo, kao drvo bresta.

162
00:22:58,924 --> 00:23:02,883
Olmo D'Alco, sin Oscara
i Rosine Cop.

163
00:23:05,361 --> 00:23:08,600
Oscar? Umro je pre 4 godine!

164
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:11,959
Nije bitno.
I mrtav se potuje.

165
00:23:13,798 --> 00:23:15,678
Kakva ste vi pseta!

166
00:23:17,037 --> 00:23:22,634
Doe leto, vrlo toplo bee

167
00:23:22,634 --> 00:23:28,233
dva deaka se zajedno rodie.

168
00:23:28,233 --> 00:23:30,112
Hajde, pij!

169
00:23:34,191 --> 00:23:37,590
Grbavom se nije dopalo!

170
00:23:40,588 --> 00:23:43,906
Sudbina se poigrala.

171
00:23:43,947 --> 00:23:48,785
Gazdinski sin i kopile seljako.

172
00:24:13,975 --> 00:24:17,254
Leo, to i ti ne jae?

173
00:24:17,254 --> 00:24:19,572
Ne penjem se ja na tog avola.

174
00:24:39,685 --> 00:24:45,362
Pa, pokosio sam 3 hektara
za 10 minuta, sve sam.

175
00:24:45,362 --> 00:24:48,722
estorici ljudi treba 6 sati.

176
00:24:48,722 --> 00:24:52,081
I misli da si dobro proao?

177
00:24:52,521 --> 00:24:56,719
G. Giovanni, vidite slamu
koja je ostala za vama...

178
00:24:56,719 --> 00:25:00,278
Nije to nita.
Ne veruje mi, zar ne?

179
00:25:00,278 --> 00:25:03,797
Ovo je iz inostranstva,
bandoglavi.

180
00:25:03,837 --> 00:25:07,075
Mi smo prvi u Bassi koji
imaju mehanike grabulje.

181
00:25:07,115 --> 00:25:11,113
Blaena neka su poslednja.
Ovo ima zube kao hijena.

182
00:25:17,232 --> 00:25:19,430
Bei, Nina, ili e te uhvatiti!

183
00:25:59,814 --> 00:26:03,573
- 19!
- Muka mi je od tebe!

184
00:26:35,043 --> 00:26:38,120
20! 20!

185
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:42,558
ekaj, da vidi.

186
00:26:50,436 --> 00:26:53,115
Poljubi, poljubi!
-Idi doavola!

187
00:26:54,514 --> 00:26:59,313
Olmo je kiopile!
Olmo je kopile!

188
00:26:59,313 --> 00:27:02,951
Olmo je kopile!

189
00:27:07,230 --> 00:27:08,828
Olmo je kopile!

190
00:27:09,909 --> 00:27:12,027
Jedi!

191
00:27:13,107 --> 00:27:17,145
Kukavice!
- Bei, seronjo!

192
00:27:17,145 --> 00:27:21,144
Samo devojice ume da plai!

193
00:27:21,184 --> 00:27:25,382
Ako si hrabar, radi to i ja.
- Hrabar sam!

194
00:27:25,382 --> 00:27:27,342
A ti, idi doavola!

195
00:27:30,459 --> 00:27:32,380
Kukavice.

196
00:28:29,039 --> 00:28:30,917
ta to radi?

197
00:28:30,957 --> 00:28:32,877
Jebem zemlju.

198
00:28:55,788 --> 00:29:00,227
ta sad radi?
- ujem oca kako mi govori.

199
00:29:02,786 --> 00:29:05,224
U telegrafskom stubu?

200
00:29:13,821 --> 00:29:16,101
Ja nita ne ujem.

201
00:29:23,976 --> 00:29:27,975
Jesi li ti blesav?
-Da vidimo ko je hrabar, a ko seka-persa.

202
00:29:35,133 --> 00:29:40,410
Kad voz naie zatvori oi,
ili e oslepeti.

203
00:29:40,410 --> 00:29:44,010
Sad nema beanja!
- Pusti me!

204
00:29:45,408 --> 00:29:47,329
Kukavice!

205
00:29:49,287 --> 00:29:51,407
Olmo! Olmo!

206
00:30:11,639 --> 00:30:13,559
Olmo!

207
00:30:15,117 --> 00:30:17,038
Jesi li mrtav, ili ta?

208
00:30:18,517 --> 00:30:23,195
Ding-dong, ding-dong.
Doavola s tim, ubij gazdu!

209
00:30:34,671 --> 00:30:37,910
Koliko ima odavde do
Madonne dei Prati?

210
00:30:37,910 --> 00:30:39,909
Oko tri kilometra.

211
00:30:40,508 --> 00:30:45,106
Jednom sam video voz dugaak
odavde do Madonne dei Prati.

212
00:30:45,106 --> 00:30:48,305
A moja kita se protee
do Piacenze!

213
00:30:48,386 --> 00:30:49,944
Brza je kao voz?

214
00:30:51,585 --> 00:30:56,303
Vozovi su prave maine,
a ne ona vrilica tamo.

215
00:30:56,303 --> 00:31:01,021
Ja volim da vozim vrilicu,
ti si protiv progresa!

216
00:31:02,219 --> 00:31:06,178
Manje radim, srean sam.

217
00:31:06,538 --> 00:31:10,696
ta misli, ko to plaa?
-Gazda.

218
00:31:10,737 --> 00:31:15,774
Mi plaamo maine svojim radom.

219
00:31:15,814 --> 00:31:21,251
Prvo je preneo vake na Paridu
a posle na malog.

220
00:31:23,731 --> 00:31:27,051
Pokuala sam da ga oistim,
ali stalno bei.

221
00:31:27,451 --> 00:31:32,928
Nisu samo vake! Danas je Olmo
terao moju Ninu da jede ivu abu.

222
00:31:32,928 --> 00:31:38,406
...a ta zna ti o filosofiji? Nita!

223
00:31:38,406 --> 00:31:43,924
Ja sam jedini koji je otiao
na sastanak Lige,

224
00:31:43,924 --> 00:31:47,804
jer na sastanke ide samo
ako shvata stvari.

225
00:31:47,804 --> 00:31:51,640
Onda moe ii okolo
i priati o pravdi...

226
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:56,240
..u izolovanim kolibama,
gde poteni seljaci vredno rade,

227
00:31:56,281 --> 00:31:59,597
a bogata buroazija
prezire radnu snagu.

228
00:31:59,678 --> 00:32:00,639
Amen.

229
00:32:02,317 --> 00:32:03,995
Vidi ti njega!

230
00:32:20,870 --> 00:32:25,428
Ko to plae? -Rosina hoe
da poalje Olma na Bogosloviju.

231
00:32:25,428 --> 00:32:28,267
Zato?
-Jer je avo!

232
00:32:32,906 --> 00:32:38,703
Hoe sina da mi uzmu,
da naprave popa od njega!

233
00:32:39,703 --> 00:32:44,022
Htela si da se igra?
Sad plai!

234
00:32:44,062 --> 00:32:49,459
Ostavi je, to je bilo davno!

235
00:32:49,459 --> 00:32:51,898
Sva kopilad postanu zla na kraju!

236
00:32:53,778 --> 00:32:56,978
Kopilad? Ko je kopile?

237
00:32:58,376 --> 00:33:00,934
Nema kopiladi u mojoj kui.

238
00:33:00,974 --> 00:33:05,492
Olmo je brat tvoga deteta
jer je otac jedan od nas.

239
00:33:05,492 --> 00:33:09,410
Nije li tako, Rosina?

240
00:33:10,132 --> 00:33:12,450
Reci im Rosina,
ti zna.

241
00:33:14,049 --> 00:33:16,329
Naravno da znam.
Iastina je.

242
00:33:18,609 --> 00:33:20,568
Ko bi drugi znao?

243
00:33:25,126 --> 00:33:27,044
Olmo!

244
00:33:49,637 --> 00:33:51,555
Olmo D'Alco!

245
00:34:02,113 --> 00:34:06,070
Olmo, sad si veliki deko...

246
00:34:06,149 --> 00:34:08,110
a jo piki u gae...

247
00:34:10,468 --> 00:34:16,146
Hodi. Upamti ovo,
nauie da ita i pie,

248
00:34:16,986 --> 00:34:22,304
ali uvek e biti
Olmo D'Alco, seljaki sin.

249
00:34:22,304 --> 00:34:24,224
Jadan i bedan.

250
00:34:26,182 --> 00:34:28,102
Sluie vojsku...

251
00:34:28,542 --> 00:34:33,820
i videe sveta.
Mora nauiti da slua.

252
00:34:33,860 --> 00:34:36,178
I da te u guzicu utiraju!

253
00:34:36,498 --> 00:34:41,657
Oenie se i naporno raditi
da prehrani svoju decu.

254
00:34:45,416 --> 00:34:49,013
Ali, ko e uvek biti?
- Olmo D'Alco.

255
00:34:49,013 --> 00:34:52,532
Olmo D'Alco. Seljak.

256
00:34:53,971 --> 00:34:56,810
Jasno?
Nema popova u ovoj kui.

257
00:35:01,089 --> 00:35:04,888
ta ima tu?
- Novi, moj je.

258
00:35:04,928 --> 00:35:08,526
G. Giovanni mi ga je dao
u zamenu za moje abe.

259
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:26,600
Ako je tvoj, onda je svaiji.

260
00:35:28,678 --> 00:35:29,919
Letim!

261
00:35:29,959 --> 00:35:35,316
Da leti, dok grana ne pukne,
upianko!

262
00:35:35,356 --> 00:35:39,394
Alfredo, veera je spremna!

263
00:35:45,432 --> 00:35:49,231
luaj parianina!

264
00:35:49,271 --> 00:35:54,828
"Puno ljubavi iz
Ville Lumire. Ottavio.

265
00:35:55,509 --> 00:35:57,428
Alfredo!

266
00:35:59,548 --> 00:36:03,786
"Ljubavi"!
Nismo ga videli godinu dana!

267
00:36:03,786 --> 00:36:07,944
Ovde se ne osea kao kod kue.
-Prezire nas.

268
00:36:07,944 --> 00:36:10,063
Nije tako.

269
00:36:10,183 --> 00:36:12,863
Tvoj brat Ottavio zna
kako da uiva u ivotu.

270
00:36:12,902 --> 00:36:17,661
Paris, Chez Maxime, cocotte...
mi radimo a on jede na novac!

271
00:36:17,661 --> 00:36:23,058
Nije tako. Alfredo, veera je spremna!
-Regina!

272
00:36:27,177 --> 00:36:29,255
Daj mi tanjir.
-Fine abe.

273
00:36:29,335 --> 00:36:31,135
Zaista.

274
00:36:32,294 --> 00:36:34,335
Alfredo.
- Ne elim ih.

275
00:36:34,414 --> 00:36:36,133
Jedi i ne budali.

276
00:36:41,890 --> 00:36:45,369
Muka mi je od njih!
-Sad u te istabati!

277
00:36:45,409 --> 00:36:49,248
Kad bude vojnik,
morae sve da jede!

278
00:36:49,248 --> 00:36:52,008
Lai! Proseravanje!

279
00:36:53,726 --> 00:36:57,645
ta je rekao moj brat?

280
00:36:57,645 --> 00:36:59,563
Regina.

281
00:37:05,562 --> 00:37:09,641
Ko si one devojke?
-Svaku no me pita!

282
00:37:09,641 --> 00:37:12,718
Moja sestra i njena erka, Regina.

283
00:37:18,118 --> 00:37:22,676
Alfredino... moja veera.

284
00:37:22,956 --> 00:37:25,434
Idi, pouri nazad.

285
00:37:31,752 --> 00:37:34,311
Svakog dana mu je sve loije.

286
00:37:34,350 --> 00:37:41,508
Koliko mu je ostalo?
-Hej, on je 6 godina mlai od mene!

287
00:37:41,508 --> 00:37:44,747
A ve je mrtav za tebe!

288
00:37:45,786 --> 00:37:48,906
Zamisli da Ottavio doe
na sahranu...

289
00:37:48,946 --> 00:37:53,424
...i poto je prvoroeni,
hoe da preuzme komandu?

290
00:37:53,464 --> 00:37:58,222
Ottavio je pravi gospodin kao ja.
Nisam ja roena kao opatica!

291
00:37:58,222 --> 00:38:01,661
I ja bih da budem opatica!

292
00:38:16,055 --> 00:38:18,815
Hoe li da opali?
-Da.

293
00:38:20,493 --> 00:38:25,092
Kundak na rame,
muri na desno oko,

294
00:38:25,092 --> 00:38:27,332
pogledaj kroz nian.

295
00:38:27,611 --> 00:38:30,249
Paljivo gledaj.

296
00:38:30,888 --> 00:38:33,848
Vidi ono jato lasta?
- Da.

297
00:38:33,968 --> 00:38:37,767
Crnu enku, pohlepnih oiju?
- Da.

298
00:38:37,806 --> 00:38:41,086
To je tvoja meta.
- Bang, bang!

299
00:38:41,086 --> 00:38:45,165
Pogodio si je!
Potrefio si je!

300
00:38:51,201 --> 00:38:54,480
Moj mu je doao do prosjakog tapa
i pobegao u Severnu Ameriku...

301
00:38:54,521 --> 00:39:00,197
ostavivi me bez novcam
sa erkom. Da mi nije bilo vas...

302
00:39:00,197 --> 00:39:02,918
Vie neu videti svog oca?

303
00:39:04,876 --> 00:39:08,674
On je sada tvoj novi otac.
Zar ne, Giovanni?

304
00:39:09,114 --> 00:39:13,033
Naravno, ako se ja
ne staram o njima, ko e?

305
00:39:13,033 --> 00:39:17,232
Ali, ti me stalno zove ujakom.

306
00:39:22,868 --> 00:39:27,347
Evo ih. Upucau Alcinu!
- Ne, ja u je.

307
00:39:27,347 --> 00:39:29,747
Spreman? Niani... Pali!

308
00:39:29,747 --> 00:39:32,267
Bravo, meu oi!

309
00:39:34,705 --> 00:39:37,984
Spreman? Niani... Pali!

310
00:39:40,863 --> 00:39:42,782
ta se deava?

311
00:39:43,461 --> 00:39:45,382
Ubiu te!

312
00:39:49,179 --> 00:39:51,259
Kakav drkadija...

313
00:40:00,376 --> 00:40:02,935
Idi zavri veeru!

314
00:40:03,974 --> 00:40:05,853
Odmah!

315
00:40:07,213 --> 00:40:09,811
Sram te bilo, i tebe!

316
00:40:14,649 --> 00:40:16,569
Idi jedi!

317
00:40:16,930 --> 00:40:21,488
Idiote! -Nije te sramota,
u tvojim godinama?

318
00:40:27,205 --> 00:40:33,403
Procep je meu nama,
mene i sviju vas!

319
00:40:35,362 --> 00:40:38,002
Nastavite sa svojim sranjima!

320
00:40:38,042 --> 00:40:43,479
On kupuje maine
dok sve ide doavola.

321
00:40:43,519 --> 00:40:49,276
Pokosie svoju guzicu
tom mainom, g. Moderni?

322
00:40:55,075 --> 00:40:56,994
Hajde, jedi!

323
00:41:04,431 --> 00:41:06,589
Jedi te abe,
ili e otii doavola.

324
00:41:06,589 --> 00:41:09,310
Govno jedno!

325
00:41:09,430 --> 00:41:12,429
Ko te to nauio?
- Prijatelj.

326
00:41:14,787 --> 00:41:19,624
Niko nee uzeti moju zemlju,
ni jedan kvadratni metar!

327
00:41:19,705 --> 00:41:21,945
Moe ti da pria ta hoe,
ali tvoj otac se namerio na Ottavia.

328
00:41:22,065 --> 00:41:27,662
Ovde sam jer hou posed!
Ceo! Inae...

329
00:41:27,662 --> 00:41:32,460
Ako hoe istinu, uvek
sam zavideo Ottaviu! Uvek!

330
00:41:34,700 --> 00:41:37,258
Da samo mogu to dalje od
ovih porodinih problema!

331
00:41:37,298 --> 00:41:42,817
Proivi malo! Spiskaj sav novac za
6 meseci! Svakog dana drugu enu!

332
00:41:46,254 --> 00:41:49,493
Ljubav je strela...

333
00:41:49,534 --> 00:41:57,771
koja moje rei tebi nosi...

334
00:42:01,849 --> 00:42:04,489
Jebeni zaliv.

335
00:42:18,043 --> 00:42:21,842
Jadniak. Niste trebali
da ga terate da jede.

336
00:42:21,883 --> 00:42:26,281
Moj je sin, niko mi nee govoriti
kako da ga odgajam.

337
00:42:26,281 --> 00:42:27,240
Alfredo!

338
00:42:27,600 --> 00:42:30,559
Ne brini, kad ogladni
vratie se.

339
00:42:42,553 --> 00:42:47,633
Ovo nisu vake,
ve kokoke!

340
00:42:47,752 --> 00:42:49,671
Miran budi.

341
00:42:58,308 --> 00:43:01,786
Videe, izgledae
kao pravi zavodnik.

342
00:43:01,786 --> 00:43:04,744
Ne mrdaj, miran.

343
00:43:26,658 --> 00:43:31,456
Nikada me nee nai,
otii u kod ujka Ottavia.

344
00:43:31,456 --> 00:43:37,492
Alfredo?
Alfredo, gde si?

345
00:43:39,491 --> 00:43:42,651
Vrati se kui, Alfredo!

346
00:43:45,969 --> 00:43:47,888
Hej, ti!

347
00:43:51,247 --> 00:43:53,447
Videli ste Alfreda?
- Ne.

348
00:43:54,606 --> 00:43:57,246
U krevet, elavi.

349
00:43:59,205 --> 00:44:01,123
Kasno je.

350
00:44:10,281 --> 00:44:12,759
Olmo! Olmo!

351
00:44:12,800 --> 00:44:14,118
ta ti hoe?

352
00:44:14,198 --> 00:44:17,756
Vrati se u krevet, ne mogu
da spavam kad luta nou.

353
00:44:18,878 --> 00:44:24,875
Da je moj otac ovde,
niko mi ne bi sekao kosu.

354
00:44:24,915 --> 00:44:29,993
Jednom sam ga uo kao me
doziva sa dna bunara.

355
00:44:29,993 --> 00:44:33,352
Alfredo!
- Hajde da pobegnemo zajedno!

356
00:44:38,590 --> 00:44:42,069
Takoe me zvao iz prazne
bundeve: "Olmo!"

357
00:44:43,148 --> 00:44:45,068
Alfredo!

358
00:44:45,787 --> 00:44:48,585
Zvao me i iz bureta lambrusco vina.

359
00:44:50,745 --> 00:44:52,664
Olmo!

360
00:44:53,984 --> 00:44:55,942
- Alfredo?
- Olmo!

361
00:45:29,330 --> 00:45:32,328
[ govore dijalektom]

362
00:46:16,673 --> 00:46:20,872
Hej, koijau, vraaj se!

363
00:46:20,911 --> 00:46:26,269
Kakva budala, ostavlja
konja na sred puta!

364
00:46:26,269 --> 00:46:28,988
Vraaj se odmah!

365
00:46:28,988 --> 00:46:31,707
Proklet bio!

366
00:46:46,060 --> 00:46:51,939
Nemam snage ni da
nareujem slugama.

367
00:46:59,817 --> 00:47:03,294
Sluaj... divna muzika.

368
00:47:04,574 --> 00:47:07,052
Mladi pleu,

369
00:47:07,052 --> 00:47:09,532
grle se,

370
00:47:10,012 --> 00:47:13,252
i vode ljubav u suton.

371
00:47:20,807 --> 00:47:23,567
Nema ovde mesta za matore.

372
00:48:29,421 --> 00:48:32,501
Vrue je, gazda, zar ne?

373
00:48:34,299 --> 00:48:38,138
Ko si ti?
- Ja sam Irma, erka Deline.

374
00:48:38,257 --> 00:48:42,976
Uvek sam hodala bosa,
sad su mi otekla stopala.

375
00:48:42,976 --> 00:48:47,654
Ali, fine su, zar ne?
Gazdarica mi ih je dala.

376
00:48:49,894 --> 00:48:52,654
Irma, za mnom!

377
00:49:18,884 --> 00:49:20,802
Hajde!

378
00:50:28,857 --> 00:50:31,575
Gazda?

379
00:50:37,054 --> 00:50:39,772
Gazda?

380
00:50:51,248 --> 00:50:53,166
Gazda?

381
00:50:58,004 --> 00:51:00,924
Ne brini.

382
00:51:03,164 --> 00:51:06,082
Neu te povrediti.

383
00:51:07,522 --> 00:51:08,282
uzmi.

384
00:51:12,480 --> 00:51:15,038
Plaite me.

385
00:51:26,674 --> 00:51:28,954
Pomuzi je.
-Nije vreme za muu.

386
00:51:28,954 --> 00:51:32,871
Otekla je, pomuzi je.

387
00:52:00,462 --> 00:52:03,861
Krave su pune mleka i govana.

388
00:52:04,980 --> 00:52:09,218
Svi smo mi prokleti.
Kletva je u nama.

389
00:52:10,137 --> 00:52:12,138
I sve je gore, sto si stariji.

390
00:52:13,697 --> 00:52:16,656
Zna li koja je najgora kletva?

391
00:52:16,656 --> 00:52:18,695
Nepogoda?

392
00:52:18,734 --> 00:52:23,413
Nije to kletva.

393
00:52:25,293 --> 00:52:27,811
Govna i mleko u mojoj glavi,
to je to.

394
00:52:32,889 --> 00:52:37,886
ak ni rat, ni pelagra nisu.

395
00:52:52,522 --> 00:52:55,761
Proklet je onaj kome se vie ne die.

396
00:53:09,916 --> 00:53:12,753
Mleko i govna.

397
00:53:17,031 --> 00:53:19,591
Nema svrhe.

398
00:53:29,827 --> 00:53:32,986
Nee da ovrsne.

399
00:53:39,944 --> 00:53:42,662
Gurni glavu unutra.

400
00:53:51,698 --> 00:53:55,057
G. Alfredo, niko ne moe
da muze bila.

401
00:54:02,935 --> 00:54:04,973
Vrati se na ples.

402
00:54:09,933 --> 00:54:12,811
Idi.
- Mogu li?

403
00:54:12,811 --> 00:54:15,770
Da. Idi, idi.

404
00:54:18,050 --> 00:54:24,047
Irma, kad zabava bude pri kraju...

405
00:54:25,685 --> 00:54:28,965
...reci svima da sam mrtav.
-U redu.

406
00:54:29,205 --> 00:54:32,963
Reci im da sam mrtav, ali
neka nastave da pleu.

407
00:54:37,122 --> 00:54:40,482
Upamtie? Mrtav.

408
00:54:40,482 --> 00:54:42,400
Okej.

409
00:55:05,790 --> 00:55:08,630
Gazda je mrtav!

410
00:55:08,669 --> 00:55:11,589
Gazda je mrtav!

411
00:55:14,828 --> 00:55:17,026
Da, na gazda je mrtav.

412
00:55:17,146 --> 00:55:19,466
Je li to istina?
- Ko e znati.

413
00:55:19,587 --> 00:55:22,504
Sklanjaj tu vodu!
Hajde da se svi napijemo!

414
00:55:22,624 --> 00:55:23,785
Napuni.

415
00:55:24,025 --> 00:55:26,063
Ali, gazda hoe da svi pleemo.

416
00:55:26,143 --> 00:55:28,143
I posle smrti bi da upravlja?

417
00:55:28,303 --> 00:55:30,221
Muzika!

418
00:56:16,525 --> 00:56:20,444
Da se samo vidite, g. Alfredo!

419
00:56:23,161 --> 00:56:26,240
Niste umrli kao gazda!

420
00:56:27,879 --> 00:56:31,438
A zato ste odvezali sve krave!

421
00:56:31,438 --> 00:56:33,998
Da napornije radim?

422
00:56:34,917 --> 00:56:36,836
Moda...

423
00:56:37,717 --> 00:56:39,955
Moda je istina da...

424
00:56:39,995 --> 00:56:43,594
...kad neko nema ta da radi...

425
00:56:43,594 --> 00:56:45,512
...ima previe vremena da pije.

426
00:56:45,552 --> 00:56:49,390
Od previe razmiljanja
postane aav.

427
00:56:51,911 --> 00:56:57,148
Bar smo se znali, znao sam
da ste vi taj koji vlada.

428
00:56:57,148 --> 00:57:00,467
Sad je sve u haosu!

429
00:57:02,147 --> 00:57:06,744
Ko zna kako e se sve zavriti.

430
00:57:11,302 --> 00:57:15,302
"Ja, Alfredo Berlinghieri,

431
00:57:15,580 --> 00:57:20,461
potpuno svestan i priseban

432
00:57:20,980 --> 00:57:25,299
ostavljam svo nasledstvo

433
00:57:26,338 --> 00:57:30,856
najmlaem sinu Giovanniu.

434
00:57:33,174 --> 00:57:35,654
Prvoroenom, Ottaviu...

435
00:57:37,453 --> 00:57:41,411
ta je rekao?
-"Prvoroenom, Ottaviu".

436
00:57:41,411 --> 00:57:46,289
ostavljam ivotnu rentu

437
00:57:47,170 --> 00:57:51,288
od 5.000 lira

438
00:57:51,329 --> 00:57:56,526
koju e dobiti za ivota

439
00:57:57,246 --> 00:58:01,444
od mog naslednika.

440
00:58:01,724 --> 00:58:04,763
Preko toga, ostavljam mu

441
00:58:06,162 --> 00:58:09,122
stan koji imam u gradu,

442
00:58:09,162 --> 00:58:12,881
pod uslovom da, bez greke,

443
00:58:22,397 --> 00:58:28,914
cela Kompanija Berlinghieri..."

444
00:58:29,033 --> 00:58:34,672
Vrati se na spavanje,
deki nije dobro.

445
00:58:35,072 --> 00:58:41,949
"...cela Kompanija Berlinghieri"

446
00:58:43,069 --> 00:58:45,747
Deko!

447
00:58:45,787 --> 00:58:48,547
Deka je mrtav!

448
00:58:48,587 --> 00:58:53,105
"...i 900 hektara obradivog zemljita i vila,

449
00:59:03,061 --> 00:59:06,540
mainerija i alati

450
00:59:10,298 --> 00:59:13,216
i sav kapital

451
00:59:13,738 --> 00:59:15,656
koji se sastoji od krava

452
00:59:17,255 --> 00:59:19,855
konja i svinja

453
00:59:21,613 --> 00:59:27,412
idu mom sinu Giovanniu."

454
01:00:05,236 --> 01:00:08,036
Ovaj turban...

455
01:00:08,076 --> 01:00:13,073
...mi je dao poznati lovac na tigrove.

456
01:00:27,709 --> 01:00:32,428
Ujae Ottavio, vodi me sa sobom.

457
01:00:32,428 --> 01:00:35,185
Zato, ne dopada ti se ovde?

458
01:00:35,185 --> 01:00:37,785
Svi su zlobni.

459
01:00:41,463 --> 01:00:42,902
Gde bi ti iao?

460
01:00:42,983 --> 01:00:45,662
Voleo bih da plovim.
-Jedrilicom?

461
01:00:48,941 --> 01:00:51,060
Kao ovom?

462
01:01:18,209 --> 01:01:20,129
ta to radi?

463
01:01:23,606 --> 01:01:25,686
Spusti to!
-Ne!

464
01:01:25,727 --> 01:01:28,207
Ne mora da pipa svilene bube!

465
01:01:29,765 --> 01:01:33,764
Diram ih jer mogu!
- Ti si budala!

466
01:01:37,642 --> 01:01:39,162
Ja sam ti gazda!

467
01:01:39,241 --> 01:01:42,161
Svilene bube su moje,
nije trebalo da dolazi.

468
01:01:42,281 --> 01:01:46,519
Zato? -Jer ih ja gajim.
Daj mi to!

469
01:01:46,519 --> 01:01:48,597
Zato bih?

470
01:01:50,158 --> 01:01:53,395
Svilene bube su moje.

471
01:01:54,756 --> 01:01:57,354
I suvo groe.

472
01:02:01,472 --> 01:02:04,193
I vrilica.

473
01:02:04,193 --> 01:02:06,510
I penica.

474
01:02:09,869 --> 01:02:13,828
I krave, i D'Alco familija.

475
01:02:16,907 --> 01:02:18,466
I ti si moj.

476
01:02:18,506 --> 01:02:22,105
Idi doavola, daj mi svilene bube!
- Ne!

477
01:02:22,505 --> 01:02:24,825
Idi doavola!

478
01:02:25,185 --> 01:02:27,903
Idi doavola!

479
01:02:28,542 --> 01:02:31,101
Sada ti bei! Kukavice!

480
01:02:47,976 --> 01:02:51,734
Pomozi, ili emo obojca
dobiti po guzici.

481
01:02:53,892 --> 01:02:57,971
Mogu te povrediti prstom,
kad buh hteo.

482
01:02:57,971 --> 01:03:00,770
Ne zasmejavaj me!

483
01:03:08,888 --> 01:03:10,806
Evo ti.

484
01:03:11,725 --> 01:03:14,925
Samo je jo par ostalo.
Druge su se ve ugnjezdile.

485
01:03:15,045 --> 01:03:19,402
Nisu to gnjezda, ve ahure.
Video sam to u knjizi.

486
01:03:19,402 --> 01:03:23,201
Skidaj tu odeu, sva je mokra.

487
01:03:24,601 --> 01:03:29,720
Tako je lagano...
Leptiri izlaze iz ove rupe.

488
01:03:31,599 --> 01:03:33,277
Nikada nisam video.

489
01:03:33,318 --> 01:03:37,915
Kao moja sestra. Roena je nou,
odmah je odletela.

490
01:03:39,516 --> 01:03:42,513
Zato je odletela?
-Jer je umrla.

491
01:03:45,034 --> 01:03:48,672
Kad umre, ne odleti.

492
01:03:50,271 --> 01:03:51,912
Samo te stave u zemlju.

493
01:04:01,667 --> 01:04:03,985
Boli li to?

494
01:04:04,265 --> 01:04:05,107
Boli li?

495
01:04:05,186 --> 01:04:08,224
Izgleda tvrdo.
-Pokai tvoj.

496
01:04:16,062 --> 01:04:20,620
Izgleda kao crv.
Ako ga povue, bie kao moj.

497
01:04:22,700 --> 01:04:24,898
Nee.
-Vuci jae.

498
01:04:26,179 --> 01:04:27,178
Boli.

499
01:04:27,577 --> 01:04:31,256
Gore po tebe. Ako nisi hrabar,
nisi socijalista.

500
01:04:31,297 --> 01:04:34,855
ta to znai?
-Ja sam socijalista bunih depova.

501
01:04:34,855 --> 01:04:40,054
Socijalista bunih depova?
-Nije bitno. Nita ti ne shvata.

502
01:04:40,133 --> 01:04:44,811
Hajde, uzmi ogrta.
-Ne treba mi!

503
01:04:44,811 --> 01:04:47,369
Ne ponaaj se detinjasto.

504
01:04:59,484 --> 01:05:01,565
Prestala je kia.

505
01:05:04,483 --> 01:05:07,042
Hodi da vidi.

506
01:05:10,321 --> 01:05:12,880
ta je to?
-To je grad.

507
01:05:12,919 --> 01:05:15,760
Ne moe biti. Predaleko je.

508
01:05:16,359 --> 01:05:18,719
To je grad, kunem se Bogom.

509
01:05:18,759 --> 01:05:23,237
To je Katedrala, iao sam tamo
sa ujka Ottaviom kad sam bio mali.

510
01:05:23,237 --> 01:05:28,355
Kakve visoke kue!
-Nisu kue, to su zvonici.

511
01:05:28,355 --> 01:05:30,752
Jedan se dimi!

512
01:05:32,313 --> 01:05:36,951
To je fabrika!
-Ko zna dal' oni nas vide.

513
01:05:41,390 --> 01:05:47,067
Tata! Videli smo grad! Veliki je!
-Kasnije...

514
01:05:47,067 --> 01:05:48,667
G. Giovanni,

515
01:05:48,708 --> 01:05:53,185
ne seam se ovakve oluje,
jo otkad sam se enio.

516
01:05:53,585 --> 01:05:57,384
Pozovi sve ljude, i radnike!

517
01:05:58,383 --> 01:06:01,301
Neka dou ovamo!

518
01:06:02,941 --> 01:06:05,299
- Orso!
- Orso!

519
01:06:05,299 --> 01:06:07,140
- Duro!
- Duro!

520
01:06:07,140 --> 01:06:08,978
- Ceso!
- Ceso!

521
01:06:09,018 --> 01:06:10,898
- Oreste!
- Oreste!

522
01:06:10,898 --> 01:06:12,698
- Moretto!
- Moretto!

523
01:06:12,698 --> 01:06:14,496
- Vecio!
- Vecio!

524
01:06:14,535 --> 01:06:18,334
- Bestione! Montanaro!
- Bestione, Montanaro!

525
01:06:18,334 --> 01:06:21,254
Za mnom, svi!

526
01:06:43,525 --> 01:06:47,564
Da skratim, sve smo izgubili.

527
01:06:48,163 --> 01:06:52,242
Lozu, paradajze, krompire,
zrnevlje, celu etvu.

528
01:06:52,481 --> 01:06:56,441
Zato svi moramo da se zrtvujemo.

529
01:06:59,400 --> 01:07:01,318
Zar ne, Leo?

530
01:07:05,078 --> 01:07:08,197
Dakle? Maca pojela jezik?

531
01:07:08,556 --> 01:07:11,996
Reci koliko smo penice uzgubili.

532
01:07:14,594 --> 01:07:17,752
Polovinu?
-Najmanje.

533
01:07:17,792 --> 01:07:22,950
Jednostavno je.
Moramo preiveti sa pola nadnice.

534
01:07:22,950 --> 01:07:26,949
Ali, kad je etva duplo jaa,
ne dobijamo duple nadnice.

535
01:07:27,229 --> 01:07:32,706
Iskreno, morao sam delati
u svom najboljem interesu,

536
01:07:33,547 --> 01:07:38,785
trebao bih vas sve poslati kuama,
posebno vas radnike!

537
01:07:39,544 --> 01:07:43,463
Vi ste gomila neznalica,
trebalo bi da mi zahvalite!

538
01:07:43,503 --> 01:07:48,820
Jer, jedini koji ovde
zaista gubi, sam ja!

539
01:07:51,140 --> 01:07:56,019
Osim toga, ko je gazda?
Ko upravlja ovde?

540
01:07:57,137 --> 01:07:59,057
Ti.

541
01:08:06,294 --> 01:08:09,174
Sve smo izgubili, zar me nisi uo?

542
01:08:09,174 --> 01:08:13,971
Jo si i uat!

543
01:08:37,562 --> 01:08:40,481
[ govori dijalektom ]

544
01:09:00,874 --> 01:09:03,192
Hajdemo unutra.

545
01:09:34,621 --> 01:09:36,220
Povredio si se?

546
01:09:38,378 --> 01:09:40,298
Da.

547
01:09:41,698 --> 01:09:45,497
Povreda na radu.
-Jadniak.

548
01:10:01,810 --> 01:10:04,129
Tata, nema vie palente.

549
01:10:07,608 --> 01:10:10,927
Tata, jo sam gladan.

550
01:10:10,967 --> 01:10:14,007
Zaboravieti glad.

551
01:10:59,828 --> 01:11:01,868
G. Abele?
-Da.

552
01:11:01,908 --> 01:11:04,745
Novosti iz Lige!
-ta kau?

553
01:11:04,745 --> 01:11:08,544
Kau da treba da krenemo,
pripremaju trajk.

554
01:11:08,984 --> 01:11:10,825
Gde?
- Svuda!

555
01:11:21,780 --> 01:11:25,338
Pa, ta je onda?

556
01:11:25,579 --> 01:11:28,737
Svi smo se sloili.
Svi emo trajkovati.

557
01:11:29,337 --> 01:11:31,255
trajk?

558
01:11:34,015 --> 01:11:36,934
Znate li ta to znai?

559
01:11:39,133 --> 01:11:42,772
Pitao sam da li znate ta to znai.

560
01:11:44,570 --> 01:11:46,570
Znai da vie ne morate
da radite ovim rukama.

561
01:11:46,651 --> 01:11:48,369
Dobro. Ima pravo.

562
01:11:48,928 --> 01:11:53,327
Nee sejati, nee njeti.

563
01:11:53,327 --> 01:11:57,165
Nee musti, nema vie mleka!

564
01:11:58,326 --> 01:12:01,204
Svi stoje mirno,

565
01:12:01,963 --> 01:12:07,682
u meu vremenu zemlja odumire!
Spremnio ste na to?

566
01:12:07,682 --> 01:12:09,881
Da. Evo Lige.

567
01:12:09,881 --> 01:12:11,801
Lige?

568
01:12:13,999 --> 01:12:16,360
ta je ta Liga?

569
01:12:18,078 --> 01:12:24,397
Da li vam je Liga rekla da emo
svi na kraju pasti travu?

570
01:12:24,397 --> 01:12:28,114
I da emo svi postati zli?
Ali, zaista zli!

571
01:12:29,634 --> 01:12:35,392
Rekli su vam to?
- Da. Liga je velika i jaka!

572
01:12:35,392 --> 01:12:39,310
Hoete da znate ta je Liga?

573
01:12:40,510 --> 01:12:43,629
trajk! trajk!

574
01:12:44,668 --> 01:12:54,184
trajk!
-trajk! trajk!

575
01:12:57,103 --> 01:13:00,902
Dopada mi se ova pesma.

576
01:13:05,381 --> 01:13:07,500
trajk!

577
01:13:42,727 --> 01:13:45,444
Jadnice, niko ih nije
pomuzao dva dana.

578
01:13:45,444 --> 01:13:48,204
Pa? Zar su i sluavke u trajku?

579
01:13:48,884 --> 01:13:52,442
Desolina, danas ide u selo po mleko.

580
01:13:52,442 --> 01:13:56,241
I nemoj da zastaje da pria ni sa kim!

581
01:13:57,760 --> 01:14:02,758
To je ludost! Da kupujemo mleko,
a tala nam je puna krava!

582
01:14:02,958 --> 01:14:06,757
trajkovi u netolerantno arogantni!

583
01:14:09,637 --> 01:14:12,074
Protiv su civilizovanih principa.

584
01:14:12,074 --> 01:14:17,473
Ti ljudi nemaju rezona,
ukljuujui i starca!

585
01:14:17,473 --> 01:14:20,231
Morae da odustanu.

586
01:14:20,271 --> 01:14:25,511
A krave e eksplodirati,
penica e trunuti na poljima.

587
01:14:26,110 --> 01:14:28,069
Ti, jedi!

588
01:14:29,869 --> 01:14:31,308
Sluajte:

589
01:14:32,387 --> 01:14:35,466
"Pregovori izmeu Trgovake Unije...

590
01:14:35,547 --> 01:14:37,385
...i Udruenja Agrara su propali.

591
01:14:38,585 --> 01:14:41,544
aljemo ljude na mesta trajkova.

592
01:14:41,544 --> 01:14:43,464
Odgovaramo na bojkot
bojkotovajem Lige."

593
01:14:43,543 --> 01:14:44,582
Prekini.

594
01:14:45,862 --> 01:14:47,543
Ovo je zvanini izvetaj!

595
01:14:47,582 --> 01:14:50,579
"Odgovaramo na trajk, klinem.

596
01:14:50,579 --> 01:14:53,059
Na nasilje, nasiljem.

597
01:14:53,059 --> 01:14:58,177
Bi je neophodan za suzbijanje
zverskih instinkta."

598
01:15:03,175 --> 01:15:05,895
Deda, ko su trak-brejkeri?

599
01:15:05,935 --> 01:15:10,053
Pseta koja rade kada se trajkuje.

600
01:15:10,053 --> 01:15:12,412
Zato oni ne trajkuju?

601
01:15:12,452 --> 01:15:15,811
Jer su bedniji
i gluplji od nas.

602
01:15:15,811 --> 01:15:18,650
Deda, sluaj muziku!

603
01:15:30,364 --> 01:15:32,724
Stiem!

604
01:15:32,765 --> 01:15:36,284
Ovde si i advokat?

605
01:15:36,803 --> 01:15:38,721
Dobro jutro Preasni.

606
01:15:40,962 --> 01:15:42,880
Vidi!

607
01:15:43,359 --> 01:15:46,559
Vidi kako g. Giovanni tri!

608
01:15:46,559 --> 01:15:49,798
Basetti radi sedei, jadniak!

609
01:15:51,037 --> 01:15:53,717
Onaj je Campanini!

610
01:15:53,757 --> 01:15:58,275
Ono je advokat, a dete
sa svinjskim repovima mu je erka.

611
01:15:58,275 --> 01:16:01,754
Svi trajk-brejkeri!
- Svi gazde!

612
01:16:03,432 --> 01:16:06,592
Smeni su!

613
01:16:24,824 --> 01:16:26,304
Olmo!

614
01:16:26,943 --> 01:16:28,223
Olmo!

615
01:16:29,703 --> 01:16:31,663
Doi!

616
01:16:34,823 --> 01:16:38,142
Je li to Socijalizam?

617
01:16:38,142 --> 01:16:43,743
Bogati koji se znoje i
siromani koji sede pod drvetom...

618
01:16:43,743 --> 01:16:48,343
...nita ne radei?
Predobro da potraje.

619
01:16:48,343 --> 01:16:52,903
Ima sree, Olmo D'Alco.
- Zato?

620
01:16:52,903 --> 01:16:56,103
Zato?

621
01:16:56,103 --> 01:17:00,783
Meni je trebalo 73 godine
da vidim gazde kako rade.

622
01:17:07,463 --> 01:17:11,583
Evo, dovri ovu zamku za krtice.

623
01:17:18,023 --> 01:17:19,983
Olmo.

624
01:17:21,462 --> 01:17:25,503
Uzmi neko lie,
rashladi me malo, moe?

625
01:17:34,064 --> 01:17:36,383
Vreme e se promeniti.

626
01:17:52,423 --> 01:17:56,983
Nauie me da pravim zamke?
- Umukni, probudie dedu.

627
01:18:02,344 --> 01:18:04,944
Kako moe da spava
s otvorenim oima?

628
01:18:04,944 --> 01:18:07,983
Moe on mnogo toga.
Jednom je video Garibaldija!

629
01:18:11,223 --> 01:18:14,503
Pazi se, ako te uhvate sa mnom,
dobie po guzici.

630
01:18:14,503 --> 01:18:18,463
Nee. Znaju da sam i ja socijalista.

631
01:18:20,184 --> 01:18:24,023
Doi da vidi!
Sada izgleda kao tvoj!

632
01:18:24,023 --> 01:18:27,504
ta si uradio?
-Vukao sam ga.

633
01:18:27,743 --> 01:18:30,143
Lae! Ovo si uradio.

634
01:18:30,823 --> 01:18:35,864
Nauiu te neto.
-Znam ja to. I ja sam socijalista.

635
01:19:00,383 --> 01:19:02,824
Kakav je ono oblak praine?

636
01:19:02,824 --> 01:19:06,224
Deca iz Basse.
-Kuda idu?

637
01:19:06,224 --> 01:19:11,024
Idu u Genovu, sa nama.
Da sade luk?

638
01:19:11,024 --> 01:19:15,784
Ne, poslali su ih ovde,
posle tri meseca trajka.

639
01:19:15,784 --> 01:19:20,504
Nije im ostalo nita za jelo,
pa je Crveni Krst pripremio voz...

640
01:19:20,504 --> 01:19:25,944
...za Genovu.
ivela deca Basse!

641
01:19:31,024 --> 01:19:36,064
ta ete im rei?
ekaj da razmislim.

642
01:19:36,064 --> 01:19:39,664
Reformisti hoe da vam
daju jo 10 centi na sat.

643
01:19:39,784 --> 01:19:41,183
Hoe li?

644
01:19:41,584 --> 01:19:47,104
10 centi na sat, puta 18 radnih sati...

645
01:19:47,104 --> 01:19:49,464
..izae oko milion i po!

646
01:19:49,464 --> 01:19:56,423
Idi, udavi se u kanalu!
-Polako, polomie mi vratne veze.

647
01:19:56,423 --> 01:20:02,704
Revolucionari kau da zemlja
treba da ide onima koji je obrauju...

648
01:20:02,704 --> 01:20:07,704
...i da ne treba da postoje
ni robovi ni gazde. Shvata?

649
01:20:07,984 --> 01:20:14,505
Da, uio sam i ja Itejlijanski!

650
01:20:14,505 --> 01:20:16,464
Italijanski!

651
01:20:16,825 --> 01:20:20,184
itao sam i u renjaku, takoe!
-Reniku!

652
01:20:20,184 --> 01:20:24,784
Odluio sam!
ta?

653
01:20:24,784 --> 01:20:28,545
Rei u: ivela revolucija!

654
01:20:28,545 --> 01:20:32,624
iveli revolucionari!
iveo generalni trajk!

655
01:20:32,624 --> 01:20:35,224
Urraaaaa!

656
01:20:49,945 --> 01:20:54,824
Sandrone, vidi ko dolazi. Oficir.

657
01:20:54,824 --> 01:20:58,784
ta e se sad desiti?

658
01:20:58,984 --> 01:21:03,824
Da ih nauimo pameti!
Dr motke. -Da!

659
01:21:03,824 --> 01:21:07,104
Da vidimo ta stvarno znaju.

660
01:21:07,104 --> 01:21:13,384
ta bi? Nali smo te!
U zatvor emo mi tebe!

661
01:21:13,384 --> 01:21:17,944
Dosta je sad!
-Razlaz!

662
01:21:22,704 --> 01:21:24,664
Gubi se!

663
01:21:34,825 --> 01:21:36,984
Hajde, deco!

664
01:21:47,424 --> 01:21:51,945
Nije vas sramota da se ljutite na decu?

665
01:22:01,225 --> 01:22:03,185
Rasisti trg!

666
01:22:11,305 --> 01:22:15,145
Svi ste vi korumpirani!
Mar kuama!

667
01:22:20,505 --> 01:22:22,465
Olmo!

668
01:22:23,024 --> 01:22:25,785
Olmo, tvoja torba!

669
01:23:04,465 --> 01:23:07,305
Olmo! Olmo!

670
01:23:39,265 --> 01:23:44,105
Nisam kukavica, Olmo.
Nisam kukavica.

671
01:23:46,226 --> 01:23:48,905
To je moja kua!

672
01:23:55,746 --> 01:23:59,146
Vidi! Vidi!

673
01:26:16,785 --> 01:26:20,986
Sramota Italije!
Dezerteri, izdajice!

674
01:26:20,986 --> 01:26:23,186
Izgledaju kao kriminalci!

675
01:26:23,186 --> 01:26:27,026
Treba ih sve pobiti!

676
01:26:28,746 --> 01:26:31,347
Tura! Tura!

677
01:26:31,347 --> 01:26:38,746
Olmo, i tebe su uhvatili?
Sve e nas pobiti!

678
01:26:38,826 --> 01:26:43,106
Proklet neka je kralj!
Svi nek' idu doavola!

679
01:26:45,266 --> 01:26:48,147
Olmo! Olmo!

680
01:27:54,147 --> 01:27:56,866
Regina, odlazi.

681
01:27:58,107 --> 01:28:04,066
Gubi se!
I presvuci se, rat je gotov!

682
01:28:04,066 --> 01:28:07,267
Da, Porunie!
-I zatvori vrata!

683
01:28:15,787 --> 01:28:17,747
Matori prdeu!

684
01:28:20,267 --> 01:28:22,186
Barabo jedna!

685
01:28:22,186 --> 01:28:24,147
Celso!

686
01:28:34,108 --> 01:28:36,067
Armida!

687
01:29:18,547 --> 01:29:21,548
Ne znam ta nije u redu sa mnom, oe,

688
01:29:21,548 --> 01:29:25,627
ali neu imati mira ako
ne naem tri narande ljubavi.

689
01:29:25,627 --> 01:29:31,227
Pustute me da ih potraim.
Kralj ree da je to samo ef,

690
01:29:31,227 --> 01:29:34,548
ali, poto je uvek bio uviavan..."

691
01:29:34,867 --> 01:29:37,507
Dakle? Nastavi da ita!

692
01:29:47,548 --> 01:29:49,867
Anita, ato si stala?

693
01:30:13,668 --> 01:30:16,587
Tio si sigurno Olmo.
- Jesam.

694
01:30:18,228 --> 01:30:19,987
Ko si ti?

695
01:30:19,987 --> 01:30:22,587
Anita. Anita Furlan.

696
01:30:23,708 --> 01:30:25,667
Venecijanka?

697
01:30:26,348 --> 01:30:29,707
Iz Verone.
- Verona?

698
01:30:30,547 --> 01:30:33,988
Postavili smo kamp u Veroni.
Izbeglica si?

699
01:30:34,108 --> 01:30:34,908
Da.

700
01:30:36,227 --> 01:30:39,187
Izgubila sam svu familiju.

701
01:30:44,268 --> 01:30:46,228
Idi sad.

702
01:30:46,708 --> 01:30:48,468
Mora da je teko.

703
01:30:48,468 --> 01:30:52,907
Anita, kako se zavrava?
- Nastavi!

704
01:30:52,907 --> 01:30:55,988
Molim te.
- U redu.

705
01:31:06,347 --> 01:31:08,147
Mir-no!

706
01:31:08,147 --> 01:31:10,108
Da, gospodine!
-Na mestu voljno!

707
01:31:17,109 --> 01:31:22,148
Ne prepoznaje prijatelje?
Ja sam, barabo!

708
01:31:46,748 --> 01:31:50,148
Porunie, raalovau te!

709
01:31:51,108 --> 01:31:55,748
Rat je gotov, niko
ne moe da nam nareuje sad.

710
01:32:04,228 --> 01:32:06,828
Tako te volim!

711
01:32:06,828 --> 01:32:09,588
Jel'? Poljubi me onda,
heroju moj!

712
01:32:24,148 --> 01:32:27,069
Niko nije pazio na
tvoje svilene bube.

713
01:32:27,069 --> 01:32:30,068
Ovde su samo mievi.

714
01:32:35,149 --> 01:32:37,308
Kao u rovovima.

715
01:32:46,829 --> 01:32:52,308
Sea se kad nam niko nije verovao
da smo videli grad odavde?

716
01:32:52,308 --> 01:32:55,268
Izgledao je tako blizu!

717
01:32:55,749 --> 01:32:59,109
Mogao si da vidi i rat odavde?

718
01:33:15,468 --> 01:33:18,949
Gazda kue,
neka mu je laka zemlja.

719
01:33:18,949 --> 01:33:25,508
Idi doavola sa svojim ocem,
majkom, i tako dalje.

720
01:33:38,629 --> 01:33:41,389
Olmo, vrati to.
Nije tvoje.

721
01:33:41,389 --> 01:33:44,109
Zar ne bee pola-pola?

722
01:33:44,109 --> 01:33:48,309
Olmo, mnogo toga se promenilo
dok si bio odsutan.

723
01:33:48,309 --> 01:33:50,148
Uvek su nam plaali pola etve.

724
01:33:50,148 --> 01:33:53,589
Gazda je morao da iznajmi
maine i plati nove radnke.

725
01:33:53,589 --> 01:33:56,709
Pa ta?
- Bila je loa godina.

726
01:33:58,309 --> 01:34:01,429
iveo nam na heroj!

727
01:34:01,429 --> 01:34:04,830
ak je i pola etve kraa, jer
mi smo ti koji rmbaimo!

728
01:34:04,830 --> 01:34:07,190
Nee ak ni pola-pola?

729
01:34:07,190 --> 01:34:10,029
Zanima te zato sam morao
unajmiti toliko radnika?

730
01:34:10,029 --> 01:34:14,549
Jer ste svi otili da ginete u ratu,

731
01:34:14,549 --> 01:34:20,469
- kao neki idioti.
- Tata, nema prava da to pria!

732
01:34:20,469 --> 01:34:23,710
Umukni, igraj se sa
limenim vojnikom ako hoe.

733
01:34:23,710 --> 01:34:26,908
Zna koliko me kota
da te drim kod kue?

734
01:34:26,908 --> 01:34:29,429
Koliko?

735
01:34:30,429 --> 01:34:34,909
Vie nego to vredi.
-Hteo sam da idem, nisi dozvolio!

736
01:34:34,909 --> 01:34:36,309
Naravno...

737
01:34:36,309 --> 01:34:39,908
To je prelepa sablja.

738
01:34:40,309 --> 01:34:43,750
Zaista jeste.

739
01:34:43,750 --> 01:34:47,149
Otra je, takoe.
Veoma otra.

740
01:34:47,389 --> 01:34:49,750
uj, tata!

741
01:34:50,309 --> 01:34:53,270
estitke, porunie.

742
01:34:53,829 --> 01:34:57,749
To je sve to moe?

743
01:34:59,829 --> 01:35:04,549
U tvojim godinama sam ustajao
u 4 ujutru da obiem tale.

744
01:35:04,549 --> 01:35:07,669
Ne bi trebalo to
da zaboravljate!

745
01:35:07,750 --> 01:35:10,429
Prvi sam se budio...

746
01:35:10,429 --> 01:35:15,189
i zadnji legao na spavanje.
Opovrgni to, ako ume!

747
01:35:15,549 --> 01:35:18,949
Opovrgni to!

748
01:35:18,949 --> 01:35:24,269
Dobar si ti, mali roae.
-Hvala, mogu ja i bolje.

749
01:35:26,269 --> 01:35:30,430
...da proirim farmu.
Nema vie nikakvih vrednosti!

750
01:35:30,709 --> 01:35:35,750
Potovanje, odanost Crkvi,
ljubav prema zemlji,

751
01:35:35,750 --> 01:35:38,309
lojalnost familiji i
poverenje u banke!

752
01:35:38,429 --> 01:35:39,950
Smiri se, molim te.

753
01:35:40,789 --> 01:35:45,069
I potovanje!
Potovanje! Potovanje!

754
01:35:45,390 --> 01:35:50,110
Gazda hoe da kae da
nije bilo nikoga da radi ovde,

755
01:35:50,110 --> 01:35:54,389
pa je morao da unajmi
nove maine

756
01:35:54,389 --> 01:35:59,710
koje je plaao u zrnevlju,
kao to je i sve vas.

757
01:36:00,630 --> 01:36:06,189
Maine e olakati ivot.
One su promena...

758
01:36:07,109 --> 01:36:08,990
...koja znai napredak.

759
01:36:08,990 --> 01:36:12,709
Velike su.

760
01:36:13,550 --> 01:36:15,510
Zlae li se?

761
01:36:19,589 --> 01:36:21,589
Teko je, zar ne?

762
01:36:44,310 --> 01:36:46,309
Hej, ta to radi?

763
01:36:46,589 --> 01:36:48,549
Prekini!

764
01:36:49,390 --> 01:36:53,430
Prestani! Armija te
nije niemu nauila?

765
01:36:53,430 --> 01:36:57,390
Ko je ovaj? - Attila Melanchini,
novi predradnik mog oca.

766
01:36:57,390 --> 01:37:00,190
Ja sam vojnik kao ti.

767
01:37:00,430 --> 01:37:03,350
uo si gazdu.

768
01:37:03,350 --> 01:37:08,030
Dali smo ti koliko smo mogli.

769
01:37:09,190 --> 01:37:12,790
Od sada radimo zajedno.
Inae, razumem ja tebe.

770
01:37:25,070 --> 01:37:27,190
Ne, Olmo! Olmo!

771
01:37:27,430 --> 01:37:29,190
Dosta.

772
01:37:31,590 --> 01:37:34,830
ene, jestel' ule gazdu?

773
01:37:35,510 --> 01:37:39,390
Krivi su nai mukarci,
jer su otili u rat da ginu.

774
01:37:39,390 --> 01:37:42,390
I radnika je krivica, takoe,
oni bi da rade...

775
01:37:42,390 --> 01:37:45,110
...pa jo i da budu plaeni.

776
01:37:45,110 --> 01:37:49,950
Naa je krivica, jer ogladnimo
i obolimo od pelagre!

777
01:37:49,950 --> 01:37:54,590
Takoe smo krivi jer nam
dva od tri deteta umru!

778
01:37:56,950 --> 01:37:58,950
Gazda nee da propadne...

779
01:37:58,950 --> 01:38:03,230
ako uzmemo jo malo
nae hrane i ostalo damo njemu!

780
01:38:03,230 --> 01:38:06,190
Hajde, pomozite sebi.

781
01:38:11,790 --> 01:38:15,630
Dobro pria za seljanicu.
-Ja sam uiteljica.

782
01:38:15,630 --> 01:38:19,430
Ti si prva uena devojka
koju sam imao.

783
01:38:19,430 --> 01:38:21,511
Izvinite, uiteljice.

784
01:38:23,830 --> 01:38:26,071
Lekcija je gotova?

785
01:38:28,110 --> 01:38:33,430
Evo ga glavni petao!
Kljucaj ovo!

786
01:38:33,430 --> 01:38:37,751
Pi pi pi pi!

787
01:38:37,751 --> 01:38:39,710
Dosta! Prekinite!

788
01:38:40,230 --> 01:38:42,190
U redu onda.

789
01:39:07,631 --> 01:39:09,510
ta se desilo?
Kuda ete?

790
01:39:09,510 --> 01:39:12,270
Da slavimo Svetog Martina.
Novembar 11ti.

791
01:39:12,351 --> 01:39:13,550
Mi smo izbaeni.

792
01:39:13,990 --> 01:39:17,790
Farmeri uvek iskoritavaju!

793
01:39:17,790 --> 01:39:21,190
Izbacili su nas pre isteka ugovora.

794
01:39:21,190 --> 01:39:24,031
Mi smo iz Lige.
- Berba je gotova.

795
01:39:24,031 --> 01:39:26,870
Gazda je traio neto
sramotno od mene...

796
01:39:26,870 --> 01:39:29,590
Sada ak i nae ene ele.

797
01:39:31,751 --> 01:39:33,790
Kukavica...

798
01:39:43,710 --> 01:39:47,431
Oreste, guzice tvrdoglava,
odlazi, nema svrhe!

799
01:39:47,431 --> 01:39:54,511
Moj ugovor istie za godinu dana.
Ni vojska me nee nateati da odem.

800
01:39:57,311 --> 01:40:01,311
Oreste! Oreste!

801
01:40:01,311 --> 01:40:05,272
Oreste!

802
01:40:11,551 --> 01:40:15,151
Gubi se!

803
01:40:15,470 --> 01:40:22,031
avoli u sedlu e doi i odneti sve!

804
01:40:36,951 --> 01:40:41,591
ak ni Papa... Ni Isus Hrist
lino me nee oterati!

805
01:40:41,591 --> 01:40:46,230
iveo sam ovde 40 godina.
Popizdeo sam!

806
01:40:46,471 --> 01:40:49,431
[ govori dijalektom ]

807
01:41:11,991 --> 01:41:19,032
Idem u Rim da protestvujem u gaama!

808
01:41:24,391 --> 01:41:29,471
Gubite se, kukavice!
- Idite, obraujte zemlju!

809
01:41:29,471 --> 01:41:31,551
Nauite ta to znai!

810
01:42:35,432 --> 01:42:40,312
Krajnje je vreme da se pojave.
Oni e hraniti magarce.

811
01:43:00,072 --> 01:43:02,633
Dopada mi se!

812
01:43:03,513 --> 01:43:06,312
Svriu!

813
01:43:06,752 --> 01:43:08,632
Tera me da svrim!

814
01:43:08,632 --> 01:43:13,313
Da svri... ni slon
te ne bi naterao na to.

815
01:43:15,632 --> 01:43:18,711
Treba mi pravo muko!

816
01:44:00,512 --> 01:44:03,713
U ime zakona, udaljite se od kue.

817
01:44:05,112 --> 01:44:08,072
Deca treba da mi spavaju
pod mostom?

818
01:44:08,072 --> 01:44:10,952
Spavae u zatvoru,
ako ne odete.

819
01:44:10,952 --> 01:44:14,072
to ne hapsite gazde
koji ne potuju ugovore?

820
01:44:14,072 --> 01:44:17,472
U ime zakona...
- Kog zakona?

821
01:44:17,472 --> 01:44:20,952
Zakon je na naoj strani, jer nam
ugovori istiu tek sledee godine.

822
01:44:20,952 --> 01:44:24,432
Gazde hoe da nam ukradu
celu radnu godinu!

823
01:44:26,752 --> 01:44:33,393
Teraju nas!
Siite, i vi nam trebate!

824
01:44:33,393 --> 01:44:37,473
Hajde ene, ili ete slaviti
Sv. Martina poslednji put.

825
01:44:37,473 --> 01:44:41,552
Zakon je na strani gazda!

826
01:44:41,552 --> 01:44:43,953
Oni uvek protestuju!

827
01:44:46,512 --> 01:44:52,032
Ne idite! Siite!
Trebate nam!

828
01:44:52,032 --> 01:44:54,033
Ne dajte da prou!

829
01:44:54,033 --> 01:45:00,232
Stanite! Hoe da izbace Oresta!

830
01:45:00,232 --> 01:45:05,672
Da mu pomognemo!
- Opkolite ovu kuu!

831
01:45:05,832 --> 01:45:07,673
Silazite s zaprega!

832
01:45:07,673 --> 01:45:10,232
Patrola, levo!

833
01:45:14,912 --> 01:45:17,233
Patrola, stoj!

834
01:45:19,152 --> 01:45:24,633
Kraljevska garda e ih naterati
da upamte ovu fetu.

835
01:45:37,193 --> 01:45:39,833
Sablje spremi!

836
01:45:42,353 --> 01:45:49,273
Za mnom, idemo po motke!
-Motke, brzo!

837
01:45:55,793 --> 01:45:57,953
Svi zajedno!

838
01:45:57,953 --> 01:46:01,393
ene smo, ne bojimo se

839
01:46:01,393 --> 01:46:05,273
Jer volimo svoju decu
Jer volimo svoju decu

840
