Oili, oila, Liga e rasti

845
01:46:24,553 --> 01:46:28,593
Socijalisti ele samo slobodu

846
01:46:28,593 --> 01:46:32,674
Nema slobode jer nismo sloni...

847
01:46:35,992 --> 01:46:41,633
